Key Match Events: Algeria came back from a goal down to win 5-1
Benhrahma scored a brace in the 29th and 55th minute
Aouar, Gouiri, and Amoura scored in the second half
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at the 19 May 1956 Stadium in Annaba
The win keeps Algeria at the top of Group E in the qualifiers
Others: Togo's Thibault Klidje opened the scoring for Togo in the 11th minute
